Audio::Ardour::Control version 0.2
==================================

Audio::Ardour::Control provides a facility to control the Ardour DAW
using the Open Sound Control protocol.

Please see the documentation in the module for more information.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Net::LibLO

